# InviteTeamMember.intent , MVP Customer Portal / Onboarding

mission InviteTeamMember

goal
  Invite a person to a workspace by email.

why
  Invites send email to third parties and expose a public accept endpoint, so they
  carry PII and abuse risk.

input
  workspaceId: WorkspaceId
  inviterId: UserId
  email: Email

output
  invite: Invite

guarantees
  only workspace members can invite
  invite links expire

never
  log(email)

verify
  test non-member cannot invite
